@ChattChitto
Awesome crack m8, all is clean and functional, I only have one remark:
You made automated cracking for x86 and x64 systems, but you can make this in one patch if you are using %ProgramFiles% variable instead of full path (This variable goes directly to "Program Files" on X32 or "Program Files (X86)" on X64 systems, so it will make patching easier :)
